              CAPITAL PUNISHMENT beta demo V5.0
              ---------------------------------
"CAPITAL PUNISHMENT" is the forthcoming major game release.
It has been made by "clickBOOM", the entertainment software
team of "Pxl computers" of Canada.

This is an exclusive "AGA experience 2" CD-ROM  
"one player against computer" playable preview of 
the CAPITAL PUNISHMENT. It's a "special mission" demo. 
The girl (warrior C) will give you a reward if you 
kill your enemy!


If you are experiencing problems starting this demo, 
please read the bottom part "starting the demo" carefully. 

                                                Thanks.
